{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"2803","heading":"Performance plans","label":"2803 Performance plans","identifier":"/us/usc/t39/s2803","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t39/ptIII/ch28","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft39%2Fs2803","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","Amendments2006—Subsec. (a). substituted “section 2401(e)” for “section 2401(g)” in introductory provisions.Pub. L. 109–435"],"amendments":["Amendments2006—Subsec. (a). substituted “section 2401(e)” for “section 2401(g)” in introductory provisions.Pub. L. 109–435"],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":null,"label":"a","identifier":"/us/usc/t39/s2803/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t39/s2803","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft39%2Fs2803%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t39/s2803/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t39/s2803/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft39%2Fs2803%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"establish performance goals to define the level of performance to be achieved by a program activity;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t39/s2803/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t39/s2803/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft39%2Fs2803%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"express such goals in an objective, quantifiable, and measurable form unless an alternative form is used under subsection (b);","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t39/s2803/a/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t39/s2803/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft39%2Fs2803%2Fa%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"briefly describe the operational processes, skills and technology, and the human, capital, information, or other resources required to meet the performance goals;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":null,"label":"4","identifier":"/us/usc/t39/s2803/a/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t39/s2803/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft39%2Fs2803%2Fa%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"establish performance indicators to be used in measuring or assessing the relevant outputs, service levels, and outcomes of each program activity;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"5","heading":null,"label":"5","identifier":"/us/usc/t39/s2803/a/5","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t39/s2803/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft39%2Fs2803%2Fa%2F5","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"provide a basis for comparing actual program results with the established performance goals; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"6","heading":null,"label":"6","identifier":"/us/usc/t39/s2803/a/6","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t39/s2803/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft39%2Fs2803%2Fa%2F6","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"describe the means to be used to verify and validate measured values.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":null,"label":"b","identifier":"/us/usc/t39/s2803/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t39/s2803","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft39%2Fs2803%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t39/s2803/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t39/s2803/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft39%2Fs2803%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t39/s2803/b/1/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t39/s2803/b/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft39%2Fs2803%2Fb%2F1%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a minimally effective program, and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t39/s2803/b/1/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t39/s2803/b/1","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft39%2Fs2803%2Fb%2F1%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a successful program,","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t39/s2803/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t39/s2803/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft39%2Fs2803%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"state why it is infeasible or impractical to express a performance goal in any form for the program activity.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":null,"label":"c","identifier":"/us/usc/t39/s2803/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t39/s2803","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft39%2Fs2803%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"In preparing a comprehensive and informative plan under this section, the Postal Service may aggregate, disaggregate, or consolidate program activities, except that any aggregation or consolidation may not omit or minimize the significance of any program activity constituting a major function or operation.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"d","heading":null,"label":"d","identifier":"/us/usc/t39/s2803/d","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t39/s2803","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft39%2Fs2803%2Fd","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t39/s2803/d/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t39/s2803/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft39%2Fs2803%2Fd%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the avoidance of interference with criminal prosecution; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t39/s2803/d/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t39/s2803/d","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft39%2Fs2803%2Fd%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"matters otherwise exempt from public disclosure under .section 410(c) of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}
